==English==
===Etymology 1===
Old English ''[[rysc]]'

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ʌʃ|-ʌʃ]]

====Noun====
'''rush''' (''plural'' '''rushes''')

#Any of several [[stiff]] [[aquatic]] or [[marsh]] plants of the [[genus]] ''Juncus'' having [[hollow]] or [[pithy]] stems and small flowers.
#The stem of such plants used in making [[basket]]s, [[mat]]s, the [[seat]]s of [[chair]]s, etc.

